con:testStep.name: GUI-subscription termination
con:testStep.con:description: 1. Open the Meveo Admin page and log in. 2. Go to Customers-> Subscription ,click on edit subscription1384 4. In the 'Subscription' tab click on Terminate button and choose 'Termination date' and 'Motif', then click on 'Terminate'

con:config.con:expectedResult: 1. An invoice_number will be generated. 2. Open pgAdmin and go to the the billing_invoice table. 3. Take note of the invoice_number and paste that invoice number in the next step. 4. Select Pass on this step to proceed.
